The Nameless Server</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pilerboy>pilerboy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/16/02 11:23:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4665.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   imo</span><hr size=1> In my opinion it isn't... yeah the agro proc is nice, but the ratio blows chunks and in the amount of time and/or cash you spend in actually gettin the darn thing, you could have picked up better weapons.  If you have the spare time to do it, kudos, but I value my EQ time more highly. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pilerboy>pilerboy</A> at: 12/16/02 11:25:21 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=federikoeq>Federiko EQ</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://eqfederiko.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 94<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/16/02 11:54:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4665.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://eqfederiko.homestead.com/files/colorbars.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: imo</span><hr size=1> What weapons have you bought that are better than the red blade for aggro?  SoD is 400k+ and I've never seen a BoC for sale on Prexus.<br>
<br>
If your guild isn't farming EB weapons, it's one hell of an offhander and well worth it. <p><p align="center"><font size="3"> <img border="0" src="http://spin.emich.edu/sig/fed6.jpg" width="275" height="182"><br>
