of Souls</a>></font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=draxusmt>Draxus MT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 167<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/16/02 1:52:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4665.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: imo</span><hr size=1> Agree Fed, you won't see a better taunt weapon until AoW or high end Luclin.  There is some belt in PoP in PoI, but I don't know how hard that is to get.  I'll be using my red epic for a very long time. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6347">Veteran Draxus Diablus</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Teir'Dal Warlord<br>
